Name: Gos Castle Runner
About the game: The Game Contains: - 14 normal levels (1 to 14). - 14 hard levels (1 to 14). - 14 very hard levels (1 to 14). - 14 extreme levels (1 to 14). - Purchase level mode in normal and hard (1 to 14). - Progress level mode in very hard and extreme (1 to 14). - Dark Levels. - Time Levels. The game reuses the levels with less time, life(5, 3 and 1) and more obstacles. The game has 56 levels in all.
